title: Robin Eubanks, Stefon Harris, Eric Harland Talk Jazz at Playboy Jazz Festival 2011
description: San Francisco Jazz Collective trombonist Robin Eubanks, vibraphonist Stefon Harris, and drummer Eric Harland talk the meaning of Jazz communication backstage after their Saturday, June 11, 2011 performance at the 33rd Playboy Jazz Festival at the Hollywood Bowl.
